{
  "stem": "9665.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Just wait.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I don't know if I was by myself, or with Melitta.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he took us to a bar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It couldn't have been with Melitta.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I think I went by myself, but I'm not sure about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I think Melitta was with me, but Melitta went, I think, back to the hotel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he said, we will have something to drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Must have been 12:00, 12:30.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He had a drink with me, and then he ordered pajaritos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you should know that I was still not kosher, but semi-kosker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Pajaritos are little birds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "To eat little birds, for me, was terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But this is the man who was going to help us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Not only that he was a count, but he was a general.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I had these pajaritos with him and whatever we had to drink.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Was fine with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he made some notes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He was not very well organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And he said, we must first get the women out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The men, that comes later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So, I should meet him the next day in that bar again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I met him four or five times in succession in that bar eating pajaritos, drinking whatever that was, which I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was very strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And the fourth day he said, we can't help them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Because the governor of Barcelona, the Basque land, is not a friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I will get these women transferred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He said, as they are on a list with 84 other women-- or, no, 84 including those women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We get them all transferred from the jail in Figueas to the jail in Madrid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I didn't believe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Three days later, he said they are arriving tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "My nerves were gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
